Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:02:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"為了在某日相逢的你"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，這怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撤退嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是不做無謂的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那下面有明人君和伊妮斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能發射相轉移砲不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡觀望一陣子再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底有多深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據調查 深度大約是十公里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之間每隔八百公尺就有次元歪曲防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是博士到底要接什麼人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 干兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那博士的樣子就不是普通人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不能憑這一點就斷定她是小愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加干兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，什麼嘛，什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然興奮起來?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明歐巴桑沒有打開通訊 所以我來代理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛是明人從火星\N玻色子跳躍到地球前認識的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有救出小愛造成明人的一個心理創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是小愛沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會來了 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概為了通過遺跡\N的好幾個次元歪曲防壁正在拚命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨好香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫阿姨有點過份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像媽媽… 跟媽媽的味道一樣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽好過份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰的一聲過後就跟大家一起睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大哥哥閃閃發光地就不知哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有飛行物體自上空落下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前確認當中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是鬱金香…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力場輸出功率降低20％
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重力波砲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方戰力分析終了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型相轉移爐式戰艦兩艘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一艘是"撫子"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到了嗎? 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以報一箭之仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那個豪快男兒這次要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神無月先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致電神無月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻準備出動人型與蟲型戰鬥機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐，不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星的人用鬱金香對我方突襲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此\N在附近連續發生玻色子跳躍 使遺跡活潑化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐，伊妮斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方機動兵器接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在專注於眼前的敵人 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曉得，包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力波砲發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵激鋼型以玻色子跳躍逐漸接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨…好可怕…好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後了 全力上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解，小愛妳等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥… 快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨，我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒見到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在見不到 但終究會見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是堅強的孩子對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人的長相…那人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生了什麼事也不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好像跟媽媽說話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人拜託我到了\N這裡就轉交這個東西 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人拜託的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐，小愛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢了半拍 所以才一直催你快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依妮斯的"依"就是字母的I喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是在\N殖民地被捲進明人君的玻色子跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後被拋到古代的火星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那兒被製造這遺跡的人們送回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N因為剛才的騷動又被跳躍到二十年前的沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前大家的記憶融合為一的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧 我的記憶…我的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月君也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的飛行員\N還有艦長和琉璃也都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐 自那時候恢復記憶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被丟到火星沙漠的她 因震驚而喪失記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被正在附近\N探測的NERGAL組員撿到的她終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心裡曉得，但沒有說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒救到妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了，大哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說 是因時間錯亂變成科幻片的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都好 快過來支援啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是這邊被集中攻擊很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 燕子花處於被圍毆的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐二兔者必兩頭落空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛攻比撫子好對付的另一隻是常識
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三郎太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼飛拳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 愛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別囉唆，快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼光束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕子花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沈了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉娜君 為保護夢想於火星消散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南…無…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳哭什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，不要自責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前碰到她的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛還是個小小的女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻被我連累\N回到過去吃了不少的苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成現在這樣彆扭的歐巴桑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，現在也無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，明人你也吃個飯團嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是餓了才沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，塞進去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你們幹啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在加油 我卻幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你看著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼承哥哥的遺志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦有什麼動靜了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下降到遺跡內部後依然沈默至今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致電敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上放棄遺跡 立刻投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始限時三十分 投降的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以優人部隊少校月臣元一朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證你們的安全…以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是命懸一線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦，艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會投降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打從一開始就沒打算把遺跡交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱熱鬧鬧幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧，健
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子怎麼也打不完呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這月面將成為你們的葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧，激鋼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的地獄才不是這樣哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 劍、明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海燕丈，還活著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有效，夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才阿純的熱血，三人加起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子死 一下子活的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼人V，使用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超熱血斬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在才知道\N你所深信的事物原來是這麼膚淺的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事，雪奈?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要消沈到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是大人該有的態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好，孩子氣一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…要當遙的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓撫子的四座引擎失控 把遺跡"碰"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想讓大家陪葬嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然只有艦長我留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香等一下，妳想死嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題，死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道妳自己在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會白白送命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了，死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說會死就是會死，笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們胡說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有了遺跡 戰爭就可以結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 自爆真的能破壞遺跡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然辦法只有一個 交給NERGAL吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證不會亂來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連燕子花都保不住還囉唆什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，小孩子說的話你們別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，不可以自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以拯救宇宙喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對火星的人們見死不救的我們唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 妳也會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，這倒也未必
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據伊妮斯小姐的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這遺跡是一種時光機器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說遺跡被破壞的瞬間 現在、過去、未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有玻色子跳躍將消失 一切化為烏有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會消失到什麼地步呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的方式…以我的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:14:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧，放棄吧，不要自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督\N提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我活著讓你這麼失望嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遺跡見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後被蚱蜢救了而成為俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼，提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不可以，提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳不是要自爆嗎? 這樣笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣\N我是學提督為了守護大家才要把船…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡毀滅的話歷史會改變 戰爭不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切全部會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，重要的事物也都會毀滅不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離完全收容遺跡單元還有2分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要運走的話分開還能用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為遺跡似乎沒有空間和時間的區別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有點不懂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是即使分離依然同亡這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，讓妳們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪奈她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說要當我丈夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非加油不可 還得照顧那遲鈍傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃，差不多該過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最珍貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這撫子一年多以來的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回憶就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被賦予記憶 而是靠自己贏得的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓它消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，對妳而言最珍貴的到底是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他們三十分鐘?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了，月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，敵人戰力薄弱而且又佔據在都市內…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要快點動手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有點不習慣這裝扮哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈，艦長 很適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機，激鋼型五機接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊我會想辦法 那邊就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，讓我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的能飛上撫子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個遺跡\N全部是由和鬱金香晶石一樣的組織構成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃 準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉娜小姐，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶比世界和平更重要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來全都是只顧私情的傢伙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是美好的自私任性嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳躍力場沒有產生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個，快接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個跟最初就打開力場的鬱金香不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓這麼大的船跳躍 當然需要一定的力場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此該說連我們也需要更電氣式的接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者該說是彼此黏膜的接觸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，要接吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話撫子會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百…百合香…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要就不要，絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是說這種話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 這也是逼不得已事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼不得已?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明人跟伊妮斯小姐接吻好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼光束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險，還是這麼的遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是\N只有在火星出生的人才能做玻色子跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河…博士…還有艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是遭到遺跡\N干涉的次微米機械改寫了火星人的基因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成適合玻色子跳躍的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些火星人當中有個人逃亡 有個人在追緝中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要和遙去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要保佑我們，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點下來啊，妳快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼 艦長上了你的AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，百合香 快點下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IFS啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長怎麼會有IFS…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快跳啊，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像AESTIVALIS的座艙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我滾哪裡去?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊器裡聽來像是在吵架的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在想什麼啊 到底在賭什麼氣?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為明人跟伊妮斯小姐… 小愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳胡扯什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會覺得該為伊妮斯小姐負責吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想讓時間倒流嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附註\N天河機的通信也傳送給木星的艦隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是宇宙裡的大吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份，幹嘛打我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香 我看了激鋼人3最後一集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個糟糕的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的故事…\N雖然糟糕 但我還是看得很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是激鋼人3跟激鋼人V並肩作戰的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說…你還是喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…曾經喜歡激鋼人的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信曾經堅信熱血的我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以明人喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家難得要講正經的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦，都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳的心意又如何呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…我最喜歡明人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡明人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來\N真的要接吻才能完成那玻色子跳躍嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐唬我說長大了就會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是留下許多的謎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮斯小姐收到的金屬板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有古代火星人及其文明等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正遺跡的\N演算單元已經乘撫子去了很遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星和地球間的戰爭會繼續嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少暫時風平浪靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 那些事還有機會再說吧
